org.corfudb.protocols.wireprotocol

Interface ILogData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<ILogData>, IMetadata
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LogData

    public interface ILogData
extends IMetadata, Comparable<ILogData>
    An interface to log data entries. Log data entries represent data stored in the actual log, with convenience methods for software to retrieve the stored information. Created by mwei on 8/17/16.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  ILogData.SerializationHandle
      This class provides a serialization handle, which manages the lifetime of the serialized copy of this entry.
